## Background and Motivation

Multiple APIs have been obsolete for a while and where intended to be removed, but looks like this hasn't happened yet. The ones I could easily find are:

https://github.com/dotnet/aspnetcore/blob/f0cfb58ef27c2eaaf906763951d02496ddd9d1a5/src/Mvc/Mvc.TagHelpers/src/ImageTagHelper.cs#L93-L105

https://github.com/dotnet/aspnetcore/blob/f0cfb58ef27c2eaaf906763951d02496ddd9d1a5/src/Mvc/Mvc.TagHelpers/src/ImageTagHelper.cs#L58-L70

https://github.com/dotnet/aspnetcore/blob/f0cfb58ef27c2eaaf906763951d02496ddd9d1a5/src/Mvc/Mvc.Core/src/CompatibilityVersion.cs#L40-L43

https://github.com/dotnet/aspnetcore/blob/f0cfb58ef27c2eaaf906763951d02496ddd9d1a5/src/Mvc/Mvc.Abstractions/src/ModelBinding/Metadata/ModelMetadataIdentity.cs#L46-L50

